// Rule Name: detecting tick escape character in posh 
// Rule Description:  Can be used for obfuscation // If one more layer of escape characters is addedtoâ€¢ the sarnple command, powershell.exe would throw an error since it does not treat the caret as an escape character cmd.exe but rather uses the tick character ( for escaping. https://www.fireeye.com/content/darn/fireeye-www/blog/pdfs/dosfuscation-report.pdf page 11 
Sysmon
| where EventID == 1
| where CommandLine matches regex '[^\s]`[^\s]//'  
